Title: Who's Your Daddy?
Plot: A 16-year-old Hurricane Katrina victim suffering from hallucinations as a result of the tragedy is brought to House by his former bandmate who recently found out the girl is his daughter. Although House fears his friend is being scammed, he takes the case. As he works his way through the girl's lies so he can diagnose and treat her, he's forced to tell a few lies of his own.
GuestStars: D.B. Sweeney, Krista Lewis, Owen Pearce, Tuffet Schmelzle, Christopher Carley, Aasha Davis, America Olivo
